data.title: Oliver Parker Movies and TV Shows on Netflix
data.meta_description:
Oliver Parker is a director born on September  6, 1960. 
		Below, you can find a list of all the movies and series featuring Oliver Parker available on Netflix.
data.text:
Dorian Gray

2009 1 h 52 min

Seduced into the decadent world of Lord Henry Wotton, handsome young aristocrat Dorian Gray becomes obsessed with maintaining his youthful appearance, and commissions a special portrait that will weather the winds of time while he remains forever young. When Gray's obsession spirals out of control, his desperate attempts to safeguard his secret turn his once-privileged life into a living hell.

6.2 IMDb

Johnny English Reborn

2011 1 h 41 min

The most prominent heads of state in the world begin gathering for a conference that could have a major impact on global politics. When MI-7 receives word that the Chinese premier has become the target of some high-powered killers, it falls on Johnny English to save the day. Armed with the latest high-tech weaponry and gadgets that would make even James Bond jealous, the once-disgraced agent uncovers evidence of a massive conspiracy involving some of the world's most powerful organisations, and vows to redeem his tarnished reputation by stopping the killers before they can strike.

6.3 IMDb
